theorem closure_interior_union_eq_union_closure_interior
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior (A ∪ B)) =
      closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
  simpa [interior_union] using
    (Set.closure_union (s := interior A) (t := interior B))

import Mathlib
import Aesop

theorem interior_union {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    interior A ∪ interior B ⊆ interior (A ∪ B) := by
  intro x hx
  cases hx with
  | inl hA =>
      have h_mono : interior A ⊆ interior (A ∪ B) :=
        interior_mono (Set.subset_union_left : (A : Set X) ⊆ A ∪ B)
      exact h_mono hA
  | inr hB =>
      have h_mono : interior B ⊆ interior (A ∪ B) :=
        interior_mono (Set.subset_union_right : (B : Set X) ⊆ A ∪ B)
      exact h_mono hB

theorem Set.closure_union {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (A ∪ B : Set X) = closure A ∪ closure B := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · -- `closure (A ∪ B)` is contained in any closed set containing `A ∪ B`
    have h_closed : IsClosed (closure A ∪ closure B) := by
      exact (isClosed_closure).union isClosed_closure
    have h_sup : (A ∪ B : Set X) ⊆ closure A ∪ closure B := by
      intro x hx
      cases hx with
      | inl hA => exact Or.inl (subset_closure hA)
      | inr hB => exact Or.inr (subset_closure hB)
    exact closure_minimal h_sup h_closed
  · -- Each component of the union of closures is in `closure (A ∪ B)`
    intro x hx
    cases hx with
    | inl hA =>
        have : (closure A : Set X) ⊆ closure (A ∪ B) :=
          closure_mono (Set.subset_union_left : (A : Set X) ⊆ A ∪ B)
        exact this hA
    | inr hB =>
        have : (closure B : Set X) ⊆ closure (A ∪ B) :=
          closure_mono (Set.subset_union_right : (B : Set X) ⊆ A ∪ B)
        exact this hB

theorem interior_closure_prod_subset
    {X Y : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] [TopologicalSpace Y]
    {A : Set X} {B : Set Y} :
    interior (closure A) ×ˢ interior (closure B) ⊆
      interior (closure (A ×ˢ B)) := by
  intro z hz
  have hEq :
      interior (closure (A ×ˢ B)) =
        interior (closure A) ×ˢ interior (closure B) :=
    interior_closure_prod (X := X) (Y := Y) (A := A) (B := B)
  simpa [hEq] using hz
